data.description: Fantastic Location! Desirable Unit 50! City water! Spacious 4 bedroom 2 bath featuring a BRAND NEW Metal Roof! Impact rated slider & most windows impact rated! Enclosed Garage offering a BONUS room perfect for larger families or to entertain all your guests.  Split Floor Plan, Formal Living with an inviting Dining area off the Kitchen.  The immaculately maintained kitchen offers shaker wood cabinets, Corian hard surface countertops & newer appliances. Spacious bedrooms with newer flooring throughout. Master suite offers a spacious Walk-In Closet and Walk-in Shower.    Inside laundry room, newer Water Heater! Private Screened in Enclosure with a large backyard and Shed, PLUS a fully fenced Dog run on the left side of the property!
